      "description": "Calling all restoration enthusiasts! This vehicle is ready for a second lease on life and offers a fantastic project for anyone who loves getting their hands dirty. While it is currently in poor condition and requires significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it serves as a solid foundation for a complete rebuild or a valuable source of parts. If you're looking for a rewarding challenge, this is the perfect opportunity to bring a classic back to the road!",
