      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and it is honestly in such beautiful shape\u2014it's been kept in a garage and treated with so much love. It looks and feels practically brand new! I'm looking for a smooth sale, so I've priced it to move. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how clean it is. Drop me a message if you're interested, I'd love to show it to you! \u2728",
