    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, recently enhanced by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive folder of service records and a clean history. From the immaculate engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model. It is a collector-grade example ready for a discerning new owner.",
      "price": 46800.0,
